{"tid":1588074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[賽外檢討］對於今日沙田和你塞有啲意見想講","createTime":"2019-09-22T16:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T17:39:52.000Z","uid":132513,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"15c29541c3391345135873ac185fb57bb5defe16","tid":1588074,"uid":132513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"今日沙田有好多細路老人家係度普通行街食飯<br />\n麻煩手足大叫口號既時候順手望下有冇細路喺自己隔離<br />\n試過見到有小朋友嚇到成個彈起左 <br />\n又或者唔好咁大聲講粗口<br />\n呢啲時候家長特別敏感 好容易搞到啲淺黃/港豬嘅家長變藍<br />\n<br />\n去到圍simplylife Starbucks 嘅時候<br />\n我覺得喺出邊嗌口號其實係冇乜問題<br />\n但係要入埋去入邊叫口號 會嚇親鋪頭入邊啲人同埋員工<br />\n其實要搞佢好簡單 之前都有post講過入去齋坐唔食 <br />\n已經可以搞到佢冇生意<br />\n<br />\n但現場太多人咁樣做 我今日企喺嗰度<br />\n完全唔知可以點樣開口阻止 因為其實我唔係想阻住佢哋行動 <br />\n我只係想大家可以有一個冇咁擾民啲嘅抗爭方法 <br />\n因為而家唔係講緊私了或者打黑警 <br />\n依家係會搞到普通市民 <br />\nSorry 係現場唔敢開口 驚俾人屌左膠<br />\n<br />\n同埋其實依家唔係講緊民意逆轉 <br />\n依家係想爭取更多人嘅支持 民意係一定有<br />\n應該諗點樣將啲淺藍轉埋做黃"},{"pid":"d9ace5fd03fdfc3f21775655c909166a8cbaba15","tid":1588074,"uid":132513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"3fec3415c8e94d700feb99923912f62ed15f8621","tid":1588074,"uid":132513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"365cf5e604cc590cecb82e927bc665db3d17c09e","tid":1588074,"uid":132513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:14:02.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"3a1dc3cc32fc638be9c0df7037a1e7dde2924c49","tid":1588074,"uid":132513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:15:19.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"0062477e7674b4be47a4ef1aeaaae4066c90c14d","tid":1588074,"uid":132513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:15:32.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"76eb553d68cdeda6bed87b578f48151d2ae83884","tid":1588074,"uid":132513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:15:45.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"83dbfc07c6a923b76b825ad6e339d0c3795b28b6","tid":1588074,"uid":132513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:15:58.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"01f0a9003a2c3b83c47bc405b87db69aed2c4acc","tid":1588074,"uid":132513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:16:10.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"58cf97ffd9f599b58a4aeb4f382c3fa691d6cab3","tid":1588074,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"6bb06a64572395a74e30c95aa14bad53c4b19686","tid":1588074,"uid":132513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"44fe8dc4ceb180c4f615bf50cf25498072cd127d","tid":1588074,"uid":322124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:16:44.000Z","msg":"輕輕推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a976c14fcb2b211ee7a3336714ce1516de6942c9","tid":1588074,"uid":132513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"071cddb63900f35a667dbcbd69bd80064ea9003c","tid":1588074,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:16:58.000Z","msg":"琴日屯門都有注意到粗口問題<br />\n本來係票投民建聯香港玩撚完呢句都好似改左<br />\n<br />\n嬲還嬲，唔好失理智<br />\n可以一家大細和理非嘅場合更加要做好形象<br />\n<br />\n焗住要開戰時就難免，但盡量講少啲"},{"pid":"113be56be7523fdf67433170d83fc96fb86a50f4","tid":1588074,"uid":132513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"071cddb63900f35a667dbcbd69bd80064ea9003c","tid":1588074,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:16:58.000Z","msg":"琴日屯門都有注意到粗口問題<br />\n本來係票投